Body: Description: I can't login on my Account with my reguler password.
Wrong product chosen, reassigning after Daniel Anton's confirmation

@Daniel Anton​ This is a critical priority, critical severity ticket. Please call the customer at the number provided. Even though Aleksandra made the initial call and met the SLA, now that it's with the correct team we should treat it like it just came in critical.

What We've Learned Updated: 15-05 Pinnacle Teleservices Pvt. Ltd. customer contacted us because they are unable to log in to their account using his regular password. 

We have scheduled a remote session where we assist them with the password reset.
Next Steps Updated: 15-05 closing the case.
